 class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span></font></code></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Usually, statements are written on separate lines to make the code more readable:</font></p><div id=\"f2uebgz6l6\" data-trusted=\"1\" class=\"code-example\" data-prism-highlighted=\"1\" style=\"margin: 22px 0px;\"><div class=\"codebox code-example__codebox\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 76px; position: relative; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; overflow: auto;\"><div class=\"toolbar codebox__toolbar\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 0px; right: 0px; z-index: 9; opacity: 0.8; display: table-row;\"><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/structure#\" title=\"run\" data-action=\"run\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_run\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></div><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/structure#\" title=\"open in sandbox\" target=\"_blank\" data-action=\"edit\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_edit\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom;