ss=\"token string\" style=\"\">\'Hello\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\'World\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span></font></code></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Here, JavaScript interprets the line break as an “implicit” semicolon. This is called an&nbsp;<a href=\"https://tc39.github.io/ecma262/#sec-automatic-semicolon-insertion\">automatic semicolon insertion</a>.</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In most cases, a newline implies a semicolon. But “in most cases” does not mean “always”!</font></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">There are cases when a newline does not mean a semicolon. For example:</font></p><div id=\"8efyx2qgxa\" data-trusted=\"1\" class=\"code-example\" data-prism-highlighted=\"1\" style=\"margin: 22px 0px;\"><div class=\"codebox code-example__codebox\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 98px; position: relative; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; overflow: auto;\"><div class=\"toolbar codebox__toolbar\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 0px; right: 0px; z-index: 9; opacity: 0.8; display: table-row;\"><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/structure#\" title=\"run\" data-action=\"run\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_run\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></div><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/structure#\" title=\"open in sandbox\" target=\"_blank\" data-action=\"edit\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_edit\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></div></div><div class=\"codebox__code\" data-code=\"1\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 98px;\"><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-javascript\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 800px; height: 98px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; counter-reset: e 0; display: flex; flex-direction: row; z-index: 0; text-shadow: none;\"><span class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"pointer-events: none; width: auto; letter-spacing: -1px; border: 0px; user-select: none; padding: 1em 0px 0.8em; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ;\"><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span></span><code class=\" language-javascript\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 1em 1em 1em 0.5em; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 0.3em; z-index: 1; text-shadow: none; margin: 0px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; flex-grow: 1;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token number\" style=\"\">3</span> <span class=\"token operator\" style=\"\">+</span>\r\n<span class=\"token number\" style=\"\">1</span>\r\n<span class=\"token operator\" style=\"\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\" style=\"\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span></font></code></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The code outputs&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">6</code>&nbsp;because JavaScript does not insert semicolons here. It is intuitively obvious that if the line ends with a plus&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">\"+\"</code>, then it is an “incomplete expression”, so a semicolon there would be incorrect. And in this case, that works as intended.</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">But there are situations where JavaScript “fails” to assume a semicolon where it is really needed.</font></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Errors which occur in such cases are quite hard to find and fix.</font></p><div class=\"important important_smart\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px; border: 3px solid var(--borderImportant); border-radius: 6px;\"><div class=\"important__header\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 24px 24px 0px; border: none;\"><span class=\"important__type\" style=\"font-weight: 700; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">An example of an error</font></span></div><div class=\"important__content\" style=\"margin: 12px 24px 24px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">If you’re curious to see a concrete example of such an error, check this code out:</font></p><div id=\"fdf4krea2x\" data-trusted=\"1\" class=\"code-example\" data-prism-highlighted=\"1\" style=\"margin: 22px 0px;\"><div class=\"codebox code-example__codebox\" style=\"width: 746px; height: 98px; position: relative; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; overflow: auto;\"><div class=\"toolbar codebox__toolbar\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 0px; right: 0px; z-index: 9; opacity: 0.8; display: table-row;\"><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/structure#\" title=\"run\" data-action=\"run\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_run\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></div><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/structure#\" title=\"open in sandbox\" target=\"_blank\" data-action=\"edit\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_edit\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></div></div><div class=\"codebox__code\" data-code=\"1\" style=\"width: 746px; height: 98px;\"><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-javascript\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 746px; height: 98px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; counter-reset: e 0; display: flex; flex-direction: row; z-index: 0; text-shadow: none;\"><span class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"pointer-events: none; width: auto; letter-spacing: -1px; border: 0px; user-select: none; padding: 1em 0px 0.8em; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ;\"><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span></span><code class=\" language-javascript\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 1em 1em 1em 0.5em; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 0.3em; z-index: 1; text-shadow: none; margin: 0px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; flex-grow: 1;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\"Hello\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">[</span><span class=\"token number\" style=\"\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\" style=\"\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">.</span><span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">forEach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span>alert<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span></font></code></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">No need to think about the meaning of the brackets&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">[]</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">forEach</code>&nbsp;yet. We’ll study them later. For now, just remember the result of running the code: it shows&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">Hello</code>, then&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">1</code>, then&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">2</code>.</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Now let’s remove the semicolon after the&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">alert</code>:</font></p><div id=\"716acngex7\" data-trusted=\"1\" class=\"code-example\" data-prism-highlighted=\"1\" style=\"margin: 22px 0px;\"><div class=\"codebox code-example__codebox\" style=\"width: 746px; height: 98px; position: relative; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; overflow: auto;\"><div class=\"toolbar codebox__toolbar\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 0px; right: 0px; z-index: 9; opacity: 0.8; display: table-row;\"><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/structure#\" title=\"run\" data-action=\"run\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_run\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></div><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/structure#\" title=\"open in sandbox\" target=\"_blank\" data-action=\"edit\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_edit\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></div></div><div class=\"codebox__code\" data-code=\"1\" style=\"width: 746px; height: 98px;\"><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-javascript\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 746px; height: 98px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; counter-reset: e 0; display: flex; flex-direction: row; z-index: 0; text-shadow: none;\"><span class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"pointer-events: none; width: auto; letter-spacing: -1px; border: 0px; user-select: none; padding: 1em 0px 0.8em; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ;\"><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span></span><code class=\" language-javascript\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 1em 1em 1em 0.5em; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 0.3em; z-index: 1; text-shadow: none; margin: 0px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; flex-grow: 1;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\"Hello\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">[</span><span class=\"token number\" style=\"\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\" style=\"\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">.</span><span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">forEach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span>alert<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span></font></code></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The difference compared to the code above is only one character: the semicolon at the end of the first line is gone.</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">If we run this code, only the first&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">Hello</code>&nbsp;shows (and there’s an error, you may need to open the console to see it). There are no numbers any more.</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">That’s because JavaScript does not assume a semicolon before square brackets&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">[...]</code>. So, the code in the last example is treated as a single statement.</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Here’s how the engine sees it:</font></p><div id=\"he0a2yjw6t\" data-trusted=\"1\" class=\"code-example\" data-prism-highlighted=\"1\" style=\"margin: 22px 0px;\"><div class=\"codebox code-example__codebox\" style=\"width: 746px; height: 54px; position: relative; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; overflow: auto;\"><div class=\"toolbar codebox__toolbar\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 0px; right: 0px; z-index: 9; opacity: 0.8; display: table-row;\"><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/structure#\" title=\"run\" data-action=\"run\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_run\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></div><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/structure#\" title=\"open in sandbox\" target=\"_blank\" data-action=\"edit\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_edit\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></div></div><div class=\"codebox__code\" data-code=\"1\" style=\"width: 746px; height: 54px;\"><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-javascript\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 746px; height: 54px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; counter-reset: e 0; display: flex; flex-direction: row; z-index: 0; text-shadow: none;\"><span class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"pointer-events: none; width: auto; letter-spacing: -1px; border: 0px; user-select: none; padding: 1em 0px 0.8em; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ;\"><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span></span><code class=\" language-javascript\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 1em 1em 1em 0.5em; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 0.3em; z-index: 1; text-shadow: none; margin: 0px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; flex-grow: 1;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\"Hello\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">[</span><span class=\"token number\" style=\"\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\" style=\"\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">.</span><span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">forEach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span>alert<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span></font></code></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Looks weird, right? Such merging in this case is just wrong. We need to put a semicolon after&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">alert</code>&nbsp;for the code to work correctly.</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">This can happen in other situations also.</font></p></div></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">We recommend putting semicolons between statements even if they are separated by newlines. This rule is widely adopted by the community. Let’s note once again –&nbsp;<em>it is possible</em>&nbsp;to leave out semicolons most of the time. But it’s safer – especially for a beginner – to use them.</font></p><h2 style=\"margin: 24px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px; font-family: BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; position: relative; break-after: avoid;\"><a class=\"main__anchor\" name=\"code-comments\" href=\"https://javascript.info/structure#code-comments\" style=\"outline: 0px; font: inherit;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Comments</font></a></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; break-before: avoid;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">As time goes on, programs become more and more complex. It becomes necessary to add&nbsp;<em>comments</em>&nbsp;which describe what the code does and why.</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Comments can be put into any place of a script. They don’t affect its execution because the engine simply ignores them.</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">One-line comments start with two forward slash characters&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">//</code>.</font></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The rest of the line is a comment. It may occupy a full line of its own or follow a statement.</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Like here:</font></p><div id=\"vj3uy8eg6p\" data-trusted=\"1\" class=\"code-example\" data-prism-highlighted=\"1\" style=\"margin: 22px 0px;\"><div class=\"codebox code-example__codebox\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 120px; position: relative; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; overflow: auto;\"><div class=\"toolbar codebox__toolbar\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 0px; right: 0px; z-index: 9; opacity: 0.8; display: table-row;\"><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/structure#\" title=\"run\" data-action=\"run\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_run\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></div><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/structure#\" title=\"open in sandbox\" target=\"_blank\" data-action=\"edit\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_edit\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></div></div><div class=\"codebox__code\" data-code=\"1\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 120px;\"><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-javascript\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 800px; height: 120px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; counter-reset: e 0; display: flex; flex-direction: row; z-index: 0; text-shadow: none;\"><span class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"pointer-events: none; width: auto; letter-spacing: -1px; border: 0px; user-select: none; padding: 1em 0px 0.8em; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ;\"><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span></span><code class=\" language-javascript\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 1em 1em 1em 0.5em; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 0.3em; z-index: 1; text-shadow: none; margin: 0px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; flex-grow: 1;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"token comment\" style=\"\">// This comment occupies a line of its own</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\'Hello\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\'World\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\" style=\"\">// This comment follows the statement</span></font></code></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Multiline comments start with a forward slash and an asterisk&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">/*</code>&nbsp;and end with an asterisk and a forward slash&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">*/</code>.</font></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Like this:</font></p><div id=\"cl65rj29hj\" data-trusted=\"1\" class=\"code-example\" data-prism-highlighted=\"1\" style=\"margin: 22px 0px;\"><div class=\"codebox code-example__codebox\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 142px; position: relative; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; overflow: auto;\"><div class=\"toolbar codebox__toolbar\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 0px; right: 0px; z-index: 9; opacity: 0.8; display: table-row;\"><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/structure#\" title=\"run\" data-action=\"run\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_run\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></div><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/structure#\" title=\"open in sandbox\" target=\"_blank\" data-action=\"edit\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_edit\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></div></div><div class=\"codebox__code\" data-code=\"1\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 142px;\"><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-javascript\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 800px; height: 142px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; counter-reset: e 0; display: flex; flex-direction: row; z-index: 0; text-shadow: none;\"><span class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"pointer-events: none; width: auto; letter-spacing: -1px; border: 0px; user-select: none; padding: 1em 0px 0.8em; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ;\"><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span></span><code class=\" language-javascript\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 1em 1em 1em 0.5em; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 0.3em; z-index: 1; text-shadow: none; margin: 0px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; flex-grow: 1;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"token comment\" style=\"\">/* An example with two messages.\r\nThis is a multiline comment.\r\n*/</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\'Hello\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\'World\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span></font></code></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The content of comments is ignored, so if we put code inside&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">/* … */</code>, it won’t execute.</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Sometimes it can be handy to temporarily disable a part of code:</font></p><div id=\"hh1eu7jo5b\" data-trusted=\"1\" class=\"code-example\" data-prism-highlighted=\"1\" style=\"margin: 22px 0px;\"><div class=\"codebox code-example__codebox\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 120px; position: relative; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; overflow: auto;\"><div class=\"toolbar codebox__toolbar\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 0px; right: 0px; z-index: 9; opacity: 0.8; display: table-row;\"><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/structure#\" title=\"run\" data-action=\"run\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_run\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></div><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/structure#\" title=\"open in sandbox\" target=\"_blank\" data-action=\"edit\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_edit\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></div></div><div class=\"codebox__code\" data-code=\"1\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 120px;\"><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-javascript\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 800px; height: 120px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; counter-reset: e 0; display: flex; flex-direction: row; z-index: 0; text-shadow: none;\"><span class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"pointer-events: none; width: auto; letter-spacing: -1px; border: 0px; user-select: none; padding: 1em 0px 0.8em; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ;\"><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span></span><code class=\" language-javascript\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 1em 1em 1em 0.5em; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 0.3em; z-index: 1; text-shadow: none; margin: 0px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; flex-grow: 1;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"token comment\" style=\"\">/* Commenting out the code\r\nalert(\'Hello\');\r\n*/</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\'World\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span></font></code></pre></div></div></div><div class=\"important important_smart\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px; border: 3px solid var(--borderImportant); border-radius: 6px;\"><div class=\"important__header\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 24px 24px 0px; border: none;\"><span class=\"important__type\" style=\"font-weight: 700; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Use hotkeys!</font></span></div><div class=\"important__content\" style=\"margin: 12px 24px 24px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In most editors, a line of code can be commented out by pressing the&nbsp;<kbd class=\"shortcut\" style=\"background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(232, 230, 229); border-radius: 2px; padding: 1px 3px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; line-height: inherit; word-spacing: -0.4ex;\">Ctrl<span class=\"shortcut__plus\" style=\"\">+</span>/</kbd>&nbsp;hotkey for a single-line comment and something like&nbsp;<kbd class=\"shortcut\" style=\"background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(232, 230, 229); border-radius: 2px; padding: 1px 3px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; line-height: inherit; word-spacing: -0.4ex;\">Ctrl<span class=\"shortcut__plus\" style=\"\">+</span>Shift<span class=\"shortcut__plus\" style=\"\">+</span>/</kbd>&nbsp;– for multiline comments (select a piece of code and press the hotkey). For Mac, try&nbsp;<kbd class=\"shortcut\" style=\"background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(232, 230, 229); border-radius: 2px; padding: 1px 3px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; line-height: inherit; word-spacing: -0.4ex;\">Cmd</kbd>&nbsp;instead of&nbsp;<kbd class=\"shortcut\" style=\"background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(232, 230, 229); border-radius: 2px; padding: 1px 3px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; line-height: inherit; word-spacing: -0.4ex;\">Ctrl</kbd>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<kbd class=\"shortcut\" style=\"background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(232, 230, 229); border-radius: 2px; padding: 1px 3px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; line-height: inherit; word-spacing: -0.4ex;\">Option</kbd>&nbsp;instead of&nbsp;<kbd class=\"shortcut\" style=\"background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(232, 230, 229); border-radius: 2px; padding: 1px 3px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; line-height: inherit; word-spacing: -0.4ex;\">Shift</kbd>.</font></p></div></div><div class=\"important important_warn\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px; border: 3px solid var(--borderImportant); border-radius: 6px;\"><div class=\"important__header\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 24px 24px 0px; border: none;\"><span class=\"important__type\" style=\"font-weight: 700; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Nested comments are not supported!</font></span></div><div class=\"important__content\" style=\"margin: 12px 24px 24px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">There may not be&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">/*...*/</code>&nbsp;inside another&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">/*...*/</code>.</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Such code will die with an error:</font></p><div id=\"n8zlunnno5\" data-trusted=\"1\" class=\"code-example\" data-prism-highlighted=\"1\" style=\"margin: 22px 0px;\"><div class=\"codebox code-example__codebox\" style=\"width: 746px; height: 120px; position: relative; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; overflow: auto;\"><div class=\"toolbar codebox__toolbar\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 0px; right: 0px; z-index: 9; opacity: 0.8; display: table-row;\"><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/structure#\" title=\"run\" data-action=\"run\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_run\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></div><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/structure#\" title=\"open in sandbox\" target=\"_blank\" data-action=\"edit\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_edit\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></div></div><div class=\"codebox__code\" data-code=\"1\" style=\"width: 746px; height: 120px;\"><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-javascript\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 746px; height: 120px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; counter-reset: e 0; display: flex; flex-direction: row; z-index: 0; text-shadow: none;\"><span class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"pointer-events: none; width: auto; letter-spacing: -1px; border: 0px; user-select: none; padding: 1em 0px 0.8em; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ;\"><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span></span><code class=\" language-javascript\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 1em 1em 1em 0.5em; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 0.3em; z-index: 1; text-shadow: none; margin: 0px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; flex-grow: 1;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"token comment\" style=\"\">/*\r\n  /* nested comment ?!? */</span>\r\n<span class=\"token operator\" style=\"\">*</span><span class=\"token operator\" style=\"\">/</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span> <span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\'World\'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span></font></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Please, don’t hesitate to comment your code.</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Comments increase the overall code footprint, but that’s not a problem at all. There are many tools which minify code before publishing to a production server. They remove comments, so they don’t appear in the working scripts. Therefore, comments do not have negative effects on production at all.</font></p></div></article></div>');
INSERT INTO `text_lesson_translations` (`id`, `text_lesson_id`, `locale`, `title`, `summary`, `content`) VALUES
(63, 75, 'en', 'The modern mode, \"use strict\"', 'For a long time, JavaScript evolved without compatibility issues. New features were added to the language while old functionality didn’t change.\r\n\r\nThat had the benefit of never breaking existing code. But the downside was that any mistake or an imperfect decision made by JavaScript’s creators got stuck in the language forever.\r\n\r\nThis was the case until 2009 when ECMAScript 5 (ES5) appeared. It added new features to the language and modified some of the existing ones. To keep the old code working, most such modifications are off by default. You need to explicitly enable them with a special directive: \"use strict\".', '<header class=\"main__header\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 16px; font-family: &quot;system-ui&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><div class=\"main__header-inner\" style=\"\"><h1 class=\"main__header-title\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: auto; padding: 0px; break-after: avoid; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 32px; line-height: 40px; font-family: BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">The modern mode, \"use strict\"</font></span></h1></div></header><div class=\"content\" style=\"font-family: &quot;system-ui&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><article class=\"formatted\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/TechArticle\" style=\"\"><div itemprop=\"author\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\" style=\"\"></div><div itemprop=\"articleBody\" style=\"\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">For a long time, JavaScript evolved without compatibility issues. New features were added to the language while old functionality didn’t change.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">That had the benefit of never breaking existing code. But the downside was that any mistake or an imperfect decision made by JavaScript’s creators got stuck in the language forever.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">This was the case until 2009 when ECMAScript 5 (ES5) appeared. It added new features to the language and modified some of the existing ones. To keep the old code working, most such modifications are off by default. You need to explicitly enable them with a special directive:&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">\"use strict\"</code>.</font></span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 24px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px; font-family: BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; position: relative; break-after: avoid;\"><a class=\"main__anchor\" name=\"use-strict\" href=\"https://javascript.info/strict-mode#use-strict\" style=\"outline: 0px; font: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">“use strict”</font></a></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; break-before: avoid;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">The directive looks like a string:&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">\"use strict\"</code>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">\'use strict\'</code>. When it is located at the top of a script, the whole script works the “modern” way.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">For example:</font></span></p><div id=\"nlf4qfndz3\" data-trusted=\"1\" class=\"code-example\" data-prism-highlighted=\"1\" style=\"margin: 22px 0px;\"><div class=\"codebox code-example__codebox\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 120px; position: relative; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; overflow: auto;\"><div class=\"codebox__code\" data-code=\"1\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 120px;\"><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-javascript\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 800px; height: 120px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; counter-reset: e 0; display: flex; flex-direction: row; z-index: 0; text-shadow: none;\"><span class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"pointer-events: none; width: auto; letter-spacing: -1px; border: 0px; user-select: none; padding: 1em 0px 0.8em; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ;\"><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span></span><code class=\" language-javascript\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 1em 1em 1em 0.5em; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 0.3em; z-index: 1; text-shadow: none; margin: 0px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; flex-grow: 1;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\"use strict\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\" style=\"\">// this code works the modern way</span>\r\n<span class=\"token operator\" style=\"\">...</span></font></span></code></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Quite soon we’re going to learn functions (a way to group commands), so let’s note in advance that&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">\"use strict\"</code>&nbsp;can be put at the beginning of a function. Doing that enables strict mode in that function only. But usually people use it for the whole script.</font></span></p><div class=\"important important_warn\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px; border: 3px solid var(--borderImportant); border-radius: 6px;\"><div class=\"important__header\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 24px 24px 0px; border: none;\"><span class=\"important__type\" style=\"font-weight: 700; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Ensure that “use strict” is at the top</font></span></div><div class=\"important__content\" style=\"margin: 12px 24px 24px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Please make sure that&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">\"use strict\"</code>&nbsp;is at the top of your scripts, otherwise strict mode may not be enabled.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Strict mode isn’t enabled here:</font></span></p><div id=\"3pvqep9fiw\" data-trusted=\"1\" class=\"code-example\" data-no-strict=\"1\" data-prism-highlighted=\"1\" style=\"margin: 22px 0px;\"><div class=\"codebox code-example__codebox\" style=\"width: 746px; height: 164px; position: relative; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; overflow: auto;\"><div class=\"codebox__code\" data-code=\"1\" style=\"width: 746px; height: 164px;\"><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-javascript\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 746px; height: 164px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; counter-reset: e 0; display: flex; flex-direction: row; z-index: 0; text-shadow: none;\"><span class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"pointer-events: none; width: auto; letter-spacing: -1px; border: 0px; user-select: none; padding: 1em 0px 0.8em; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ;\"><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span></span><code class=\" language-javascript\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 1em 1em 1em 0.5em; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 0.3em; z-index: 1; text-shadow: none; margin: 0px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; flex-grow: 1;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\"some code\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token comment\" style=\"\">// \"use strict\" below is ignored--it must be at the top</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\"use strict\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\" style=\"\">// strict mode is not activated</span></font></span></code></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Only comments may appear above&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">\"use strict\"</code>.</font></span></p></div></div><div class=\"important important_warn\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px; border: 3px solid var(--borderImportant); border-radius: 6px;\"><div class=\"important__header\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 24px 24px 0px; border: none;\"><span class=\"important__type\" style=\"font-weight: 700; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">There’s no way to cancel&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">use strict</code></font></span></div><div class=\"important__content\" style=\"margin: 12px 24px 24px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">There is no directive like&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">\"no use strict\"</code>&nbsp;that reverts the engine to old behavior.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Once we enter strict mode, there’s no going back.</font></span></p></div></div><h2 style=\"margin: 24px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px; font-family: BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; position: relative; break-after: avoid;\"><a class=\"main__anchor\" name=\"browser-console\" href=\"https://javascript.info/strict-mode#browser-console\" style=\"outline: 0px; font: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Browser console</font></a></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; break-before: avoid;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">When you use a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://javascript.info/devtools\">developer console</a>&nbsp;to run code, please note that it doesn’t&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">use strict</code>&nbsp;by default.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Sometimes, when&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">use strict</code>&nbsp;makes a difference, you’ll get incorrect results.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">So, how to actually&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">use strict</code>&nbsp;in the console?</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">First, you can try to press&nbsp;<kbd class=\"shortcut\" style=\"background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(232, 230, 229); border-radius: 2px; padding: 1px 3px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; line-height: inherit; word-spacing: -0.4ex;\">Shift<span class=\"shortcut__plus\" style=\"\">+</span>Enter</kbd>&nbsp;to input multiple lines, and put&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">use strict</code>&nbsp;on top, like this:</font></span></p><div id=\"9n2atnrekr\" data-trusted=\"1\" class=\"code-example\" data-prism-highlighted=\"1\" style=\"margin: 22px 0px;\"><div class=\"codebox code-example__codebox\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 98px; position: relative; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; overflow: auto;\"><div class=\"codebox__code\" data-code=\"1\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 98px;\"><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-javascript\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 800px; height: 98px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; counter-reset: e 0; display: flex; flex-direction: row; z-index: 0; text-shadow: none;\"><span class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"pointer-events: none; width: auto; letter-spacing: -1px; border: 0px; user-select: none; padding: 1em 0px 0.8em; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ;\"><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span></span><code class=\" language-javascript\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 1em 1em 1em 0.5em; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 0.3em; z-index: 1; text-shadow: none; margin: 0px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; flex-grow: 1;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\'use strict\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span> <span class=\"token operator\" style=\"\">&lt;</span>Shift<span class=\"token operator\" style=\"\">+</span>Enter <span class=\"token keyword\" style=\"\">for</span> a newline<span class=\"token operator\" style=\"\">&gt;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token comment\" style=\"\">//  ...your code</span>\r\n<span class=\"token operator\" style=\"\">&lt;</span>Enter to run<span class=\"token operator\" style=\"\">&gt;</span></font></span></code></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">It works in most browsers, namely Firefox and Chrome.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">If it doesn’t, e.g. in an old browser, there’s an ugly, but reliable way to ensure&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">use strict</code>. Put it inside this kind of wrapper:</font></span></p><div id=\"9taszqu6an\" data-trusted=\"1\" class=\"code-example\" data-prism-highlighted=\"1\" style=\"margin: 22px 0px;\"><div class=\"codebox code-example__codebox\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 142px; position: relative; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; overflow: auto;\"><div class=\"codebox__code\" data-code=\"1\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 142px;\"><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-javascript\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 800px; height: 142px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; counter-reset: e 0; display: flex; flex-direction: row; z-index: 0; text-shadow: none;\"><span class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"pointer-events: none; width: auto; letter-spacing: -1px; border: 0px; user-select: none; padding: 1em 0px 0.8em; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ;\"><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span></span><code class=\" language-javascript\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 1em 1em 1em 0.5em; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 0.3em; z-index: 1; text-shadow: none; margin: 0px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; flex-grow: 1;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\" style=\"\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\'use strict\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span>\r\n\r\n  <span class=\"token comment\" style=\"\">// ...your code here...</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span></font></span></code></pre></div></div></div><h2 style=\"margin: 24px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px; font-family: BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; position: relative; break-after: avoid;\"><a class=\"main__anchor\" name=\"should-we-use-strict\" href=\"https://javascript.info/strict-mode#should-we-use-strict\" style=\"outline: 0px; font: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Should we “use strict”?</font></a></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; break-before: avoid;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">The question may sound obvious, but it’s not so.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">One could recommend to start scripts with&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">\"use strict\"</code>… But you know what’s cool?</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Modern JavaScript supports “classes” and “modules” – advanced language structures (we’ll surely get to them), that enable&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">use strict</code>&nbsp;automatically. So we don’t need to add the&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">\"use strict\"</code>&nbsp;directive, if we use them.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">So, for now&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">\"use strict\";</code>&nbsp;is a welcome guest at the top of your scripts. Later, when your code is all in classes and modules, you may omit it.</font></strong></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">As of now, we’ve got to know about&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">use strict</code>&nbsp;in general.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">In the next chapters, as we learn language features, we’ll see the differences between the strict and old modes. Luckily, there aren’t many and they actually make our lives better.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">All examples in this tutorial assume strict mode unless (very rarely) specified otherwise.</font></span></p></div></article></div>');
