kground-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 0.3em; z-index: 1; text-shadow: none; margin: 0px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; flex-grow: 1;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span class=\"token keyword\" style=\"\">const</span> birthday <span class=\"token operator\" style=\"\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\'18.04.1982\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\" style=\"\">const</span> age <span class=\"token operator\" style=\"\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">someCode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span>birthday<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span></font></span></code></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"margin: 18px 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Here we have a constant&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">birthday</code>&nbsp;for the date, and also the&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">age</code>&nbsp;constant.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin: 18px 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">The&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">age</code>&nbsp;is calculated from&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">birthday</code>&nbsp;using&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">someCode()</code>, which means a function call that we didn’t explain yet (we will soon!), but the details don’t matter here, the point is that&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">age</code>&nbsp;is calculated somehow based on the&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">birthday</code>.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin: 18px 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Would it be right to use upper case for&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">birthday</code>? For&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">age</code>? Or even for both?</font></span></p><div id=\"2vp4fv1z1h\" data-trusted=\"1\" class=\"code-example\" data-prism-highlighted=\"1\" style=\"margin: 18px 0px;\"><div class=\"codebox code-example__codebox\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 98px; position: relative; margin: 18px 0px; overflow: auto;\"><div class=\"codebox__code\" data-code=\"1\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 98px;\"><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-javascript\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 800px; height: 98px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; counter-reset: e 0; display: flex; flex-direction: row; z-index: 0; text-shadow: none;\"><span class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"pointer-events: none; width: auto; letter-spacing: -1px; border: 0px; user-select: none; padding: 1em 0px 0.8em;\"><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span></span><code class=\" language-javascript\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 1em 1em 1em 0.5em; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 0.3em; z-index: 1; text-shadow: none; margin: 0px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; flex-grow: 1;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span class=\"token keyword\" style=\"\">const</span> <span class=\"token constant\" style=\"\">BIRTHDAY</span> <span class=\"token operator\" style=\"\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\'18.04.1982\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\" style=\"\">// make birthday uppercase?</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\" style=\"\">const</span> <span class=\"token constant\" style=\"\">AGE</span> <span class=\"token operator\" style=\"\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">someCode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token constant\" style=\"\">BIRTHDAY</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\" style=\"\">// make age uppercase?</span></font></span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>');
