(66, 78, 'en', 'Interaction: alert, prompt, confirm', 'Interaction: alert, prompt, confirm\r\nAs we’ll be using the browser as our demo environment, let’s see a couple of functions to interact with the user: alert, prompt and confirm.', '<header class=\"main__header\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 16px; font-family: &quot;system-ui&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><div class=\"main__header-inner\" style=\"\"><h1 class=\"main__header-title\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: auto; padding: 0px; break-after: avoid; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 32px; line-height: 40px; font-family: BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Interaction: alert, prompt, confirm</font></span></h1></div></header><div class=\"content\" style=\"font-family: &quot;system-ui&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><article class=\"formatted\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/TechArticle\" style=\"\"><div itemprop=\"author\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\" style=\"\"></div><div itemprop=\"articleBody\" style=\"\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">As we’ll be using the browser as our demo environment, let’s see a couple of functions to interact with the user:&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">alert</code>,&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">prompt</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">confirm</code>.</font></span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 24px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px; font-family: BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; position: relative; break-after: avoid;\"><a class=\"main__anchor\" name=\"alert\" href=\"https://javascript.info/alert-prompt-confirm#alert\" style=\"outline: 0px; font: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">alert</font></a></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; break-before: avoid;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">This one we’ve seen already. It shows a message and waits for the user to press “OK”.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">For example:</font></span></p><div id=\"3d4ylj7892\" data-trusted=\"1\" class=\"code-example\" data-prism-highlighted=\"1\" style=\"margin: 22px 0px;\"><div class=\"codebox code-example__codebox\" style=\"width