le=\"\">confirm</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span>question<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span></font></span></code></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">The function&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">confirm</code>&nbsp;shows a modal window with a&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">question</code>&nbsp;and two buttons: OK and Cancel.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">The result is&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">true</code>&nbsp;if OK is pressed and&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">false</code>&nbsp;otherwise.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">For example:</font></span></p><div id=\"5ac9cr4an0\" data-trusted=\"1\" class=\"code-example\" data-prism-highlighted=\"1\" style=\"margin: 22px 0px;\"><div class=\"codebox code-example__codebox\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 98px; position: relative; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; overflow: auto;\"><div class=\"toolbar codebox__toolbar\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 0px; right: 0px; z-index: 9; opacity: 0.8; display: table-row;\"><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/alert-prompt-confirm#\" title=\"run\" data-action=\"run\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_run\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></span></div><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/alert-prompt-confirm#\" title=\"open in sandbox\" target=\"_blank\" data-action=\"edit\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_edit\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></span></div></div><div class=\"codebox__code\" data-code=\"1\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 98px;\"><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-javascript\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 800px; height: 98px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; counter-reset: e 0; display: flex; flex-direction: row; z-index: 0; text-shadow: none;\"><span class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"pointer-events: none; width: auto; letter-spacing: -1px; border: 0px; user-select: none; padding: 1em 0px 0.8em; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ;\"><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span></span><code class=\" language-javascript\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 1em 1em 1em 0.5em; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 0.3em; z-index: 1; text-shadow: none; margin: 0px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; flex-grow: 1;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span class=\"token keyword\" style=\"\">let</span> isBoss <span class=\"token operator\" style=\"\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">confirm</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\"Are you the boss?\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span> isBoss <span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\" style=\"\">// true if OK is pressed</span></font></span></code></pre></div></div></div><h2 style=\"margin: 24px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px; font-family: BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; position: relative; break-after: avoid;\"><a class=\"main__anchor\" name=\"summary\" href=\"https://javascript.info/alert-prompt-confirm#summary\" style=\"outline: 0px; font: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Summary</font></a></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; break-before: avoid;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">We covered 3 browser-specific functions to interact with visitors:</font></span></p><dl style=\"margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px;\"><dt><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">alert</font></code></dt><dd style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">shows a message.</font></span></dd><dt><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">prompt</font></code></dt><dd style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">shows a message asking the user to input text. It returns the text or, if Cancel button or&nbsp;<kbd class=\"shortcut\" style=\"background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(232, 230, 229); border-radius: 2px; padding: 1px 3px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; line-height: inherit; word-spacing: -0.4ex;\">Esc</kbd>&nbsp;is clicked,&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">null</code>.</font></span></dd><dt><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">confirm</font></code></dt><dd style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">shows a message and waits for the user to press “OK” or “Cancel”. It returns&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">true</code>&nbsp;for OK and&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">false</code>&nbsp;for Cancel/<kbd class=\"shortcut\" style=\"background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(232, 230, 229); border-radius: 2px; padding: 1px 3px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; line-height: inherit; word-spacing: -0.4ex;\">Esc</kbd>.</font></span></dd></dl><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">All these methods are modal: they pause script execution and don’t allow the visitor to interact with the rest of the page until the window has been dismissed.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">There are two limitations shared by all the methods above:</font></span></p><ol style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 21px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0.3em 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">The exact location of the modal window is determined by the browser. Usually, it’s in the center.</font></span></li><li style=\"margin: 0.3em 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">The exact look of the window also depends on the browser. We can’t modify it.</font></span></li></ol><p style=\"margin: 12px 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">That is the price for simplicity. There are other ways to show nicer windows and richer interaction with the visitor, but if “bells and whistles” do not matter much, these methods work just fine.</font></span></p></div></article></div>');
