on\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token number\" style=\"\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\" style=\"\">// false</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span> <span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\"hello\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\" style=\"\">// true</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span> <span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\" style=\"\">// false</span></font></span></code></pre></div></div></div><div class=\"important important_warn\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px; border: 3px solid var(--borderImportant); border-radius: 6px;\"><div class=\"important__header\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 24px 24px 0px; border: none;\"><span class=\"important__type\" style=\"font-weight: 700; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Please note: the string with zero&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">\"0\"</code>&nbsp;is&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">true</code></font></span></div><div class=\"important__content\" style=\"margin: 12px 24px 24px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Some languages (namely PHP) treat&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">\"0\"</code>&nbsp;as&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">false</code>. But in JavaScript, a non-empty string is always&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">true</code>.</font></span></p><div id=\"h9tikrr12f\" data-trusted=\"1\" class=\"code-example\" data-prism-highlighted=\"1\" style=\"margin: 22px 0px;\"><div class=\"codebox code-example__codebox\" style=\"width: 746px; height: 76px; position: relative; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; overflow: auto;\"><div class=\"toolbar codebox__toolbar\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 0px; right: 0px; z-index: 9; opacity: 0.8; display: table-row;\"><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/type-conversions#\" title=\"run\" data-action=\"run\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_run\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></span></div><div class=\"toolbar__tool\" style=\"display: table-cell; padding-left: 1px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\"><a href=\"https://javascript.info/type-conversions#\" title=\"open in sandbox\" target=\"_blank\" data-action=\"edit\" class=\"toolbar__button toolbar__button_edit\" style=\"padding: 0px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 30px; height: 30px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px;\"></a></font></span></div></div><div class=\"codebox__code\" data-code=\"1\" style=\"width: 746px; height: 76px;\"><pre class=\"line-numbers  language-javascript\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 746px; height: 76px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; counter-reset: e 0; display: flex; flex-direction: row; z-index: 0; text-shadow: none;\"><span class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"pointer-events: none; width: auto; letter-spacing: -1px; border: 0px; user-select: none; padding: 1em 0px 0.8em; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ;\"><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span><span style=\"pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: e 1;\"></span></span><code class=\" language-javascript\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 1em 1em 1em 0.5em; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 0.3em; z-index: 1; text-shadow: none; margin: 0px; direction: ltr; word-spacing: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; position: relative; flex-grow: 1;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span> <span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\"0\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\" style=\"\">// true</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span> <span class=\"token function\" style=\"\">Boolean</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">(</span><span class=\"token string\" style=\"\">\" \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\" style=\"\">// spaces, also true (any non-empty string is true)</span></font></span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div><h2 style=\"margin: 24px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px; font-family: BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; position: relative; break-after: avoid;\"><a class=\"main__anchor\" name=\"summary\" href=\"https://javascript.info/type-conversions#summary\" style=\"outline: 0px; font: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Summary</font></a></h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; break-before: avoid;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">The three most widely used type conversions are to string, to number, and to boolean.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\"><strong><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">String Conversion</code></strong>&nbsp;– Occurs when we output something. Can be performed with&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">String(value)</code>. The conversion to string is usually obvious for primitive values.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\"><strong><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">Numeric Conversion</code></strong>&nbsp;– Occurs in math operations. Can be performed with&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">Number(value)</code>.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">The conversion follows the rules:</font></span></p><table style=\"width: 800px; font-size: 15px; margin: 30px 0px;\"><thead><tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid var(--borderPrimary);\"><th style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 1em 2px 5px; border-bottom: 3px solid var(--borderPrimary); vertical-align: bottom;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Value</font></span></th><th style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 1em 2px 5px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 3px solid var(--borderPrimary); vertical-align: bottom;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Becomes…</font></span></th></tr></thead><tbody style=\"border: 0px;\"><tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid var(--borderPrimary);\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 1em 2px 5px;\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 2px; font-weight: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">undefined</font></code></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 1em 2px 5px;\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 2px; font-weight: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">NaN</font></code></td></tr><tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid var(--borderPrimary); background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 1em 2px 5px;\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 2px; font-weight: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">null</font></code></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 1em 2px 5px;\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 2px; font-weight: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">0</font></code></td></tr><tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid var(--borderPrimary);\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 1em 2px 5px;\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 2px; font-weight: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">true&nbsp;/&nbsp;false</font></code></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 1em 2px 5px;\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 2px; font-weight: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">1 / 0</font></code></td></tr><tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid var(--borderPrimary); background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 1em 2px 5px;\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 2px; font-weight: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">string</font></code></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 1em 2px 5px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">The string is read “as is”, whitespaces (includes spaces, tabs&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px; font-weight: inherit;\">\\t</code>, newlines&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px; font-weight: inherit;\">\\n</code>&nbsp;etc.) from both sides are ignored. An empty string becomes&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px; font-weight: inherit;\">0</code>. An error gives&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px; font-weight: inherit;\">NaN</code>.</font></span></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\"><strong><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">Boolean Conversion</code></strong>&nbsp;– Occurs in logical operations. Can be performed with&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">Boolean(value)</code>.</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Follows the rules:</font></span></p><table style=\"width: 800px; font-size: 15px; margin: 30px 0px;\"><thead><tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid var(--borderPrimary);\"><th style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 1em 2px 5px; border-bottom: 3px solid var(--borderPrimary); vertical-align: bottom;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Value</font></span></th><th style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 1em 2px 5px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 3px solid var(--borderPrimary); vertical-align: bottom;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Becomes…</font></span></th></tr></thead><tbody style=\"border: 0px;\"><tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid var(--borderPrimary);\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 1em 2px 5px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px; font-weight: inherit;\">0</code>,&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px; font-weight: inherit;\">null</code>,&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px; font-weight: inherit;\">undefined</code>,&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px; font-weight: inherit;\">NaN</code>,&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px; font-weight: inherit;\">\"\"</code></font></span></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 1em 2px 5px;\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 2px; font-weight: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">false</font></code></td></tr><tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid var(--borderPrimary); background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ;\"><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 1em 2px 5px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">any other value</font></span></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 1em 2px 5px;\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 2px; font-weight: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">true</font></code></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Most of these rules are easy to understand and memorize. The notable exceptions where people usually make mistakes are:</font></span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 22px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 21px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin: 0.3em 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">undefined</code>&nbsp;is&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">NaN</code>&nbsp;as a number, not&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">0</code>.</font></span></li><li style=\"margin: 0.3em 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\"><code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">\"0\"</code>&nbsp;and space-only strings like&nbsp;<code style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, Menlo, Monaco, monospace; padding: 2px 4px; background-image: ; background-position-x: ; background-position-y: ; background-size: ; background-repeat-x: ; background-repeat-y: ; background-attachment: ; background-origin: ; background-clip: ; border-radius: 2px;\">\" \"</code>&nbsp;are true as a boolean.</font></span></li></ul><p style=\"margin: 12px 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Objects aren’t covered here. We’ll return to them later in the chapter&nbsp;<a href=\"https://javascript.info/object-toprimitive\" style=\"\">Object to primitive conversion</a>&nbsp;that is devoted exclusively to objects after we learn more basic things about JavaScript.</font></span></p></div></article></div>');
