(70, 82, 'en', '2. Compound data structures (lists, tuples, and dictionaries)', '2. Compound data structures (lists, tuples, and dictionaries)\r\nLists and tuples (compound data types):\r\nOne of the most commonly used and important data structures in Python are lists. A list is a collection of elements, and the collection can be of the same or varied data types.\r\n\r\nUnderstanding lists will eventually pave the way for computing algebraic equations and statistical models on your array of data.', '<h2 id=\"2-compound-data-structures-lists-tuples-and-dictionaries-\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.5em 0px 0.2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.15; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 3.6rem; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; min-width: 100%;\"><font color=\"#000000\">2. Compound data structures (lists, tuples, and dictionaries)</font></h2><h3 id=\"lists-and-tuples-compound-data-types-\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.5em 0px 0.2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.15; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 2.8rem; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; min-width: 100%;\"><font color=\"#000000\">Lists and tuples (compound data types)