(73, 85, 'en', 'What is PHP?', 'Summary\r\nPHP stands for Hypertext pre-processor\r\nPHP is a server side scripting language. This means that it is executed on the server. The client applications do not need to have PHP installed.\r\nPHP files are saved with the “.php” file extension, and the PHP development code is enclosed in tags.\r\nPHP is open source and cross platform', '<h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 28px; line-height: 40px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">What is a Scripting Language?</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\">A script is a set of programming instructions that is interpreted at runtime.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\">A scripting language is a language that interprets scripts at runtime. Scripts are usually embedded into other software environments.</p><div class=\"code-block code-block-2\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; margin: 8px 0px; clear: both;\"><div align=\"center\" data-freestar-ad=\"__728x250\" id=\"guru99_incontent_1\" name=\"guru99_incontent_1\" data-google-query-id=\"CLOEpqair_8CFdComgod62MKGA\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; height: 250px;\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/24132379/guru99_incontent_1_0__container__\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0pt none; width: 728px; height: 0px;\"></div></div></div><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\">The purpose of the scripts is usually to enhance the performance or perform routine tasks for an application.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\">Server side scripts are interpreted on the server while client side scripts are interpreted by the client application.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\">PHP is a server side script that is interpreted on the server while<a href=\"https://www.guru99.com/interactive-javascript-tutorials.html\" data-lasso-id=\"187022\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-timing-function: linear;\">&nbsp;JavaScript&nbsp;</a>is an example of a client side script that is interpreted by the client browser. Both PHP and JavaScript can be embedded into HTML pages.</p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 28px; line-height: 40px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><a id=\"1\" data-lasso-id=\"187023\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(5, 86, 243); transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-timing-function: linear;\"></a>Programming Language Vs Scripting Language</h2><table class=\"table table-striped\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); margin-left: 0px; width: 837.141px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; word-break: normal; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; border-spacing: 0px !important;\"><tbody style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><th style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0.5rem; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\">Programming language</th><th style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0.5rem; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; background: rgb(249, 249, 249); text-align: left !important;\">Scripting language</th></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0.5rem; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\">Has all the features needed to develop complete applications.</td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0.5rem; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\">Mostly used for routine tasks</td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0.5rem; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\">The code has to be compiled before it can be executed</td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0.5rem; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-color: in