in-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; text-align: center; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"><a href=\"https://images/2013/04/uac_deactivated.png\" data-lasso-id=\"188551\" class=\"nohover\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-timing-function: linear;\"><img decoding=\"async\" title=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" alt=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" height=\"155\" src=\"https://www.guru99.com/images/2013/04/uac_deactivated.png\" width=\"405\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.guru99.com/images/2013/04/uac_deactivated.png\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" class=\"entered lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: inline-block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">Step 6) Click Next</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\">In the succeeding screen, click next</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; text-align: center; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"><a href=\"https://images/2013/04/xampp_install_step_1.png\" data-lasso-id=\"188552\" class=\"nohover\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-timing-function: linear;\"><img decoding=\"async\" title=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" alt=\"Download and Install X