lasso-id=\"188557\" class=\"nohover\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-timing-function: linear;\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"208\" height=\"322\" title=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" alt=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" src=\"https://www.guru99.com/images/2013/04/xampp_directories.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.guru99.com/images/2013/04/xampp_directories.png\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" class=\"entered lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: inline-block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; text-align: center; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"></p><ul style=\"margin: 0 0 var(--global-md-spacing); padding: 0px 0px 0px 2em; list-style: disc; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">htdocs</span>; this is the web root directory. All of our PHP codes will be placed in this directory.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">mysql</span>&nbsp;– this directory contains all the information related to MySQL database engine, by default it runs on port 3306.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">php</span>&nbsp;– this directory contains PHP installation files. It contains an important file named php.ini. This directory is used to configure how PHP behaves on your server.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inh