ot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Syntax highlighting and auto-complete features enhances your&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">productivity</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">It has native support for database systems like MySQL.&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">You don’t need to use two programs to code and develop your database</span>.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">The IDE can be used in a&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">collaborative environment</span>. This comes in handy when you have to work with other developers as a team.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">The IDE has&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">support for other languages</span>&nbsp;such as;<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 2em; list-style: disc;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Java SE</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Java EE</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">C</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">C++</li></ul></li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">The current version of the Netbeans IDE as of this writing is version 7.3</span></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 28px; line-height: 40px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><a id=\"8\" data-lasso-id=\"188566\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(5, 86, 243); transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-timing-function: linear;\"></a>Introduction to Netbeans IDE</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\">After you have successfully installed the Netbeans IDE PHP editor, run the program just like any other windows program. The window shown below appears</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"><a href=\"https://images/2013/04/netbeans_ide_walk_through.png\" data-lasso-id=\"188567\" class=\"nohover\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-timing-function: linear;\"><img decoding=\"async\" title=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" alt=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://www.guru99.com/images/2013/04/netbeans_ide_walk_through.png\" width=\"1142\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.guru99.com/images/2013/04/netbeans_ide_walk_through.png\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" class=\"entered lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: inline-block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">1. Project explorer</span>&nbsp;– this panel is used to display all the opened projects. The projects are listed in a tree view.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">2. Shortcuts tool bar</span>&nbsp;– this toolbar contains shortcuts to frequently performed tasks such as creating a new project, opening an existing project, undo and redo actions etc.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">3. Startup page</span>&nbsp;– this page contains 3 tabs namely- Learn &amp; Discover, My Netbeans and What’s New.</p><ul style=\"margin: 0 0 var(--global-md-spacing); padding: 0px 0px 0px 2em; list-style: disc; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">The first tab [Learn and Discover] introduces you to the features of the Netbeans IDE, showcases some demos and tutorials that can be developed in the Netbeans IDE.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">The second tab [My Netbeans] lists the recently opened projects, allows you to install plugins and activate features of the IDE.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">4. Output window</span>&nbsp;– it is used to display output from programs such as Java console applications. It is also used to display log and debug information. The screenshot below shows the IDE with a project open.</p><div class=\"code-block code-block-4\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; margin: 8px 0px; clear: both;\"><div data-freestar-ad=\"__300x250 __336x280\" id=\"guru99_incontent_3\" name=\"guru99_incontent_3\" data-google-query-id=\"CMTF_tGir_8CFRlMwgod5FYKjg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; height: 280px;\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/24132379/guru99_incontent_3_0__container__\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0pt none; width: 234px; height: 0px;\"></div></div></div><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; text-align: center; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"><a href=\"https://images/2013/04/netbeans_ide_features.png\" data-lasso-id=\"188568\" class=\"nohover\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-timing-function: linear;\"><img decoding=\"async\" title=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" alt=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" height=\"686\" src=\"https://www.guru99.com/images/2013/04/netbeans_ide_features.png\" width=\"990\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.guru99.com/images/2013/04/netbeans_ide_features.png\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" class=\"entered lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: inline-block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\"></a></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 28px; line-height: 40px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><a id=\"9\" data-lasso-id=\"188569\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(5, 86, 243); transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-timing-function: linear;\"></a>Creating a new PHP project using the Netbeans IDE</h2><ul style=\"margin: 0 0 var(--global-md-spacing); padding: 0px 0px 0px 2em; list-style: disc; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Click on the create new project button on the tool bar as shown below</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; text-align: center; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"><a href=\"https://images/2013/04/create_new_project.png\" data-lasso-id=\"188570\" class=\"nohover\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-timing-function: linear;\"><img decoding=\"async\" title=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" alt=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" height=\"79\" src=\"https://www.guru99.com/images/2013/04/create_new_project.png\" width=\"130\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.guru99.com/images/2013/04/create_new_project.png\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" class=\"entered lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: inline-block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\"></a></p><ul style=\"margin: 0 0 var(--global-md-spacing); padding: 0px 0px 0px 2em; list-style: disc; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">If you downloaded all the bundles available in the XAMPP NetBeans IDE, make sure you choose PHP under project category, PHP Application under Projects then click on Next button.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; text-align: center; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"><a href=\"https://images/2013/04/new_project_wizard_1.png\" data-lasso-id=\"188571\" class=\"nohover\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-timing-function: linear;\"><img decoding=\"async\" title=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" alt=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" height=\"499\" src=\"https://www.guru99.com/images/2013/04/new_project_wizard_1.png\" width=\"729\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.guru99.com/images/2013/04/new_project_wizard_1.png\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" class=\"entered lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: inline-block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\"></a></p><ul style=\"margin: 0 0 var(--global-md-spacing); padding: 0px 0px 0px 2em; list-style: disc; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Enter the project name as shown below.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; text-align: center; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"><a href=\"https://images/2013/04/new_project_wizard_2.png\" data-lasso-id=\"188572\" class=\"nohover\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-timing-function: linear;\"><img decoding=\"async\" title=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" alt=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" height=\"499\" src=\"https://www.guru99.com/images/2013/04/new_project_wizard_2.png\" width=\"729\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.guru99.com/images/2013/04/new_project_wizard_2.png\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" class=\"entered lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: inline-block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\"></a></p><ul style=\"margin: 0 0 var(--global-md-spacing); padding: 0px 0px 0px 2em; list-style: disc; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Make sure the folder is saved in the XAMPP PHP installation directory as shown above.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Click on next button when done.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; text-align: center; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"><a href=\"https://images/2013/04/new_project_wizard_3.png\" data-lasso-id=\"188573\" class=\"nohover\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-timing-function: linear;\"><img decoding=\"async\" title=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" alt=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" height=\"499\" src=\"https://www.guru99.com/images/2013/04/new_project_wizard_3.png\" width=\"895\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.guru99.com/images/2013/04/new_project_wizard_3.png\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" class=\"entered lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: inline-block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\"></a></p><ul style=\"margin: 0 0 var(--global-md-spacing); padding: 0px 0px 0px 2em; list-style: disc; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">Make sure Run as: is set to Local Web Site(running on local web server)</span><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 2em; list-style: disc;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">The Project URL: is set to&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">http://localhost/phplessons/</span></li></ul></li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\"><i style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Note</i></span><i style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">&nbsp;the above settings will be set for you by default. You don’t have to change anything unless you are an expert</i></p><ul style=\"margin: 0 0 var(--global-md-spacing); padding: 0px 0px 0px 2em; list-style: disc; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Click on Next button</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; text-align: center; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"><a href=\"https://images/2013/04/new_project_wizard_4.png\" data-lasso-id=\"188574\" class=\"nohover\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-timing-function: linear;\"><img decoding=\"async\" title=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" alt=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" height=\"498\" src=\"https://www.guru99.com/images/2013/04/new_project_wizard_4.png\" width=\"889\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.guru99.com/images/2013/04/new_project_wizard_4.png\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" class=\"entered lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: inline-block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\"></a></p><ul style=\"margin: 0 0 var(--global-md-spacing); padding: 0px 0px 0px 2em; list-style: disc; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">The Netbeans PHP editor allows for integration with PHP MVC frameworks such as Symfony and Zend. For now we will not select any MVC framework. Click on Finish button.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Your newly created project will be displayed in the project browser and an index.php page created for you.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">The newly create page contains some html code. Replace it with the following code shown below.</li></ul><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 28px; line-height: 40px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><a id=\"10\" data-lasso-id=\"188575\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(5, 86, 243); transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-timing-function: linear;\"></a>Running your first PHP Example</h2><pre style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background: var(--global-palette7); font-family: &quot;Courier 10 Pitch&quot;, Courier, monospace; font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 100%; padding: 1.5em; text-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">&lt;?php\r\necho \"Hello World!\";\r\n?&gt;</pre><ul style=\"margin: 0 0 var(--global-md-spacing); padding: 0px 0px 0px 2em; list-style: disc; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Click on the run button on the toolbar as shown below</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: var(--global-md-spacing); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; text-align: center; margin-right: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px !important;\"><a href=\"https://images/2013/04/run_project.png\" data-lasso-id=\"188576\" class=\"nohover\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; transition-duration: 0.1s; transition-timing-function: linear;\"><img decoding=\"async\" title=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" alt=\"Download and Install XAMPP &amp; Netbeans\" height=\"60\" src=\"https://www.guru99.com/images/2013/04/run_project.png\" width=\"175\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.guru99.com/images/2013/04/run_project.png\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" class=\"entered lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: inline-block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\"></a></p><ul style=\"margin: 0 0 var(--global-md-spacing); padding: 0px 0px 0px 2em; list-style: disc; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Your default browser will be opened with the URL&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">http://localhost/phplessons/index.php</span>&nbsp;. The output “Hello World!” will be displayed in your browser.</li><li></li></ul>');
